OL,3,CGypsy, Roma and Traveller pupils
OL,4,Cshowcase their culture in new
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,FThe lives and traditions of children
OL,8,Ffrom Gypsy, Roma and Traveller
OL,9,Fcommunities in South Wales are being
OL,10,Fcelebrated in a new project.
OL,12,FPupils from West Monmouth School in
OL,13,FPontypool have created and curated the
OL,14,FWanderlust exhibition, which runs at
OL,15,FTorfaen Museum until the middle of
OL,16,FJuly.
OL,18,FThe scheme, launched to tie in with
OL,19,FGypsy, Roma and Traveller History
OL,20,FMonth, offers a candid insight into
OL,21,Fthe lives of the families taking part.
