OL,7,FTorfaen Traveller Education Service
OL,8,Fworks with local families to build
OL,9,Frelationships and support young people
OL,10,Fin schools.
OL,12,FSavannah Miller says she's found the
OL,13,Fsupport invaluable, and now works with
OL,14,Fthe unit herself to help other
OL,15,Ffamilies in the area.
OL,17,F"We're not just a label. We're not
OL,18,Fjust a stereotype" she says.
