OL,7,F"We are human beings and our culture
OL,8,Fis our way of life. Family, religion,
OL,9,Fand traditional values are general is
OL,10,Freally important for the traveling
OL,11,Fcommunity."
OL,13,F"It's been nice to be able to share
OL,14,F(the project) with my family because
OL,15,Fmy dad is a Traveller and I don't
OL,16,Fthink he would have ever thought that
OL,17,Fhe'd be able to do something like this
OL,18,Fto involve his community"
