OL,7,F"It's been nice to be able to see the
OL,8,Fimpact it's had on them. Even just
OL,9,Ftaking a few photos or having a few
OL,10,Fphotos taken and talking about their
OL,11,Fway of life".
OL,13,FPhotographer Jon Pountney and poet and
OL,14,Fplaywright Patrick Jones have worked
OL,15,Fwith the children to develop their
OL,16,Fskills.
OL,18,F"It was just a really fulfilling
OL,19,Fproject from the start" he says.
