OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"It was a very informal, calm
OL,8,Fenvironment (with) a little space at
OL,9,Fthe table. So it wasn't pressurised!"
OL,11,F"As you can see with some of the
OL,12,Fpoems, they're really moving. People
OL,13,Fwrote about their family, about what
OL,14,Fthey believe in in life and about how
OL,15,Fthey view the world."
OL,17,F"It's really important for our Gypsy
OL,18,Fand Traveller families to feel part of
OL,19,Fa mainstream community" says Lynne
OL,20,FRobinson, who leads the Torfaen
OL,21,FTraveller Education Service.
