OL,3,CGypsy, Roma and Traveller pupils
OL,4,Cshowcase their culture in new
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"We've got outstanding partnerships
OL,8,Fwith our local primary schools, and we
OL,9,Freally encourage all the families to
OL,10,Fengage really well.
OL,12,F"Gypsy & Traveller History Month gives
OL,13,Fus the opportunity to actually
OL,14,Fshowcase how wonderful our community
OL,15,Fis that I'm honoured to serve and also
OL,16,Fthe young people and how talented they
OL,17,Fare".
OL,19,FHer colleague Bronwyn Parker has
OL,20,Fhelped the children realise their
OL,21,Fideas.
