OL,3,CGypsy, Roma and Traveller pupils
OL,4,Cshowcase their culture in new
OL,5,Cexhibition
OL,7,F"I think at the start the pupils were
OL,8,Fpossibly nervous about how they were
OL,9,Fgoing to create some art or some
OL,10,Fpoetry, and they've actually smashed
OL,11,Fit" she says.
OL,13,F"We've looked at things like their
OL,14,Finspirations, their traditions, things
OL,15,Fthat were important to them"
OL,17,F"They've really embraced it and been
OL,18,Freally passionate about taking photos
OL,19,Fand sharing their stories and showing
OL,20,Fthe community. We're really proud!"
